SecureVector SIEM Dashboard Templates
=====================================

The files under this directory (Splunk XML, Microsoft Sentinel workbook JSON,
Grafana dashboard JSON, etc.) are MIT-licensed starter templates authored by
the SecureVector maintainers. They are provided AS-IS, with no warranty, and
are intended as a starting point for operators — NOT as finished, production-
validated detection content.

BEFORE RELYING ON THESE TEMPLATES FOR PRODUCTION DETECTION OR COMPLIANCE
REPORTING: import them into your own SIEM/observability stack, verify that
every panel renders correctly against real events, and adjust queries,
sourcetypes, table names, or data-source UIDs to match your environment.

